&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Implements best practice standards in safety management and actively promotes safety and safe working practices in all operations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
