&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;D9&lt;/strong&gt; Provide a leading role and technical expertise in the event of an emergency response situation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Speed and effectiveness of appropriate response&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K1 K5&lt;br&gt;S12&lt;br&gt;B3 B4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
